text: Héctor Zatarain (born 27 June 1929) was a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
